name: ChainEye
introduce: ChainEye is an open source full-chain analysis tool. At present, it has functions such as BridgeEye (cross-chain bridge comparison tool), On-chain&CEX transfer fee (on-chain & CEX transfer fee query), Multichain Gas (multi-chain gas fee query) and other functions, and will develop new functions such as security modules and nft modules in the future. ChainEye promises to provide users with free data services forever, and will return the income of the tool ToB to the community and users. Chaineye is Incubated by Biteye.
